{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-posts-asciidoc-page-attributes-slug-tsx","path":"/posts/mysql-config/","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"642a2057-14f9-5b67-9728-ea73fc210d6d","html":"<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_超时\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_超时\"></a>超时</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">show global variables like '%timeout%';</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>查看超时相关变量</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">set global wait_timeout=3600;</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>wait_timeout</code>: 服务器在关闭非交互式连接之前等待活动的秒数</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">set global interactive_timeout=3600;</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>interactive_timeout</code>: 服务器在关闭交互式连接之前等待活动的秒数</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_连接数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_连接数\"></a>连接数</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"literalblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre>show full processlist;</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>查看所有连接数</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">kill processlist_id;</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>kill 指定连接线程</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">show variables like '%max_connections%';</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>查看最大连接数</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-mysql\" data-lang=\"mysql\">set global max_connections = 200;</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>设置最大连接数</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_参考\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_参考\"></a>参考</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/Huozhiwu_11/article/details/104530746\">Mysql连接超时解决方案1:\n修改默认超时时间</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/6689474434f7\">MySQL 连接数满情况的处理</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/server-system-variables.html\">Server\nSystem Variables</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/show-processlist.html\">SHOW\nPROCESSLIST Statement</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/kill.html\">KILL Statement</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"Mysql 设置"},"pageAttributes":{"slug":"mysql-config","category":"database"},"revision":{"date":"2021-02-08","number":"1.0"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"642a2057-14f9-5b67-9728-ea73fc210d6d","pageAttributes__slug":"mysql-config","__params":{"pageAttributes__slug":"mysql-config"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3143286284"],"slicesMap":{}}